PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 1997-892 of July 3, 1997, which will extend the term of appointment of MICHEL F. PAULO as full-time member of the Convention Refugee Determination Division of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Montreal Regional Office) until February 8, 2004; and designation of MICHEL F. PAULO as Assistant Deputy Chairperson of the Convention Refugee Determrination Division of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Montreal Regional Office).
